WEBVTT

00:04.330 --> 00:06.855
Mom, open the door! Please!

00:09.882 --> 00:13.151
Mom, open the door!

00:13.219 --> 00:15.971
Please don't, mom!
Please don't!

00:20.910 --> 00:22.861
Please don't. Please!

00:24.730 --> 00:27.916
Open the door! Please!

00:28.000 --> 00:30.168
Please don't, mom!

00:38.824 --> 00:40.724
Mom? Open the door.

00:44.363 --> 00:45.329
Mom!

00:48.233 --> 00:50.401
Open it!

00:52.737 --> 00:54.738
Mom, please.

00:56.291 --> 00:58.209
Mom...

